# Ping Agent

Inspect project control-plane health for a named agent or for `ccbd`.

## Usage

The first argument must be an agent name from `.ccb/ccb.config`, or `ccbd`.

## Execution (MANDATORY)

```powershell
ccb ping $ARGUMENTS
```

## Examples

- `/ping agent1`
- `/ping agent3`
- `/ping ccbd`
